OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1779865531
OL,3,CTeenage boy stabbed in Brighton after
OL,4,Creports of 'people fighting'
OL,6,FA teenager has been hospitalised after
OL,7,Freports of a "large group of people
OL,8,Ffighting" on Brighton seafront, police
OL,9,Fsay.
OL,11,FOfficers were called at around 9:25pm
OL,12,Fon Monday outside Shelter Hall, where
OL,13,Fa boy, from Surrey, had been stabbed.
OL,15,FSussex Police said that he was taken
OL,16,Fto hospital with superficial injuries.
OL,18,FIt is now appealing for anyone who
OL,19,Fwitnessed the alleged incident to get
OL,20,Fin touch.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
