OL,3,CTeenage boy stabbed in Brighton after
OL,4,Creports of 'people fighting'
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Jen Pietersen, of
OL,7,FBrighton CID, said: "We know the beach
OL,8,Fwas extremely crowded at the time of
OL,9,Fthis incident and we're urging anyone
OL,10,Fwho can assist in our investigation to
OL,11,Fplease come forward.
OL,13,F"Specifically, we'd like to speak to
OL,14,Fanyone who saw what happened or
OL,15,Fcaptured any relevant footage.
OL,17,F"You can report it online or via 101,
OL,18,Fquoting serial 1791 of 25/05."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
